Package: cookieCutter
Title: A template for API as a package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jamie", "Owen", , "jamie@jumpingrivers.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is an example of how a plumber API as a package might look
    and could potentially be used as a starting point for future API projects. It was predominantly
    created for the Jumping Rivers API as a package structure blog post.
